title: 2021 CFB Pick Em Week 7
description:
El Pres, Big Cat & Rico Bosco are back for another week of picks. Rico catches scrutiny for his mortal lock of Bama last week, Big Cat had more hostility on the private jet & Angelina is back to talk FCS.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/barstoolpickem
